motional hysteria of the previous decade, or a gross abdication of the Four=
th Estate=E2=80=99s responsibilities to hold power accountable. (A similar =
debate is ensuing about Meta=E2=80=99s decision to forgo fact-checking.) Ei=
ther way, it is indisputably awkward=E2=80=94<em>most </em>notably for the =
journalists whose righteous indignation was either performative then or
easily bought off now.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;"><br/>In any event, Thompso=
n=E2=80=99s decree was yet another blow to morale for a network that now si=
